今晚去了中環加州大廈新開了一間中西合璧的餐廳叫「紅樓」，餐廳位於23樓，周著有落地玻璃窗十分開揚，可俯瞰中環景緻；裝修有彩石長枱、洋式圓枱、洋式椅子和吊燈等，並設有酒吧，可見玩味，亦有氣氛。

一行二人，各點了《珍菌黑松露球》共兩夥：
內有煙肉和蘑菇餡，外皮煙煙韌韌口感似煎堆，再加上比一般細少的黑芝麻更增添香口。
 
燒味系中點了《黑豚肉叉燒皇(例牌)》（這份是二人份量哦～）

黑豚肉叉燒放於鐵板上再用火爐滾熱，鑊氣十分又令叉燒更入味。黑豚肉叉燒果然稱得上是皇，因為厚身得來十分腍嫩並且有肉汁，毫無韌位，十分讚！

《薑汁龍鬚芥蘭》（這份都是二人份量哦～）芥蘭的菜衣已取，並且師傅用刀界過，令嫩綠清甜的芥蘭更加脆爽，而且有薑粒的薑香。

飯點有炒飯或泡飯選擇，我們就選了較濕潤的後者。

《濃湯鴨絲泡飯》亦都是原煲取出再用火爐滾熱著。湯很香濃，而飯加入了脆米和芝麻，香口又有口感，鴨絲肉多又有肉香，此泡飯不錯，份量足夠3-4人。

甜點是《杞子桂花糕》，每人兩件的份量，正常無特別。

服務：服務員細心有禮，印象不錯。

result.name: FUMI (Japanese Cuisine)

reviews.text:
Food was great and I've enjoyed our food. However, the service needs to be improved  given their target audience based on their ambience and price tag. It's a far cry compared to the quality of food. 

Attentiveness on filling up the tea needs be consistently reminded, clearing the table was up to me before the next dish is served, and General lack of awareness from the staff does not match with the target audience they are aiming for. Every detail needs to be asked before it gets done.

The only Japanese restaurant in HK which passed my raw seafood handling test. Q1 your seafood fresh? Q2 have they been deep frozen? 
Guidelines requires raw fish to be frozen at -35C for 7 hours or -20C for 7 days to kill parasites and ova.

Food is mediocre & overpriced.  Although restaurant is listed on eatigo for a huge discount during off-peak hours, staff are extremely strict about the fine print of the discount. So don’t book on eatigo and expect a discount unless you’re sure you can finish your lunch strictly within 1 hour.
Really good Japanese restaurant.  The lunch special is best value.  The miyazawa beef just melts in your mouth and the sashimi is super fresh.  Definitely a great deal

Price: $200-400pp
Quality: 👩🏻‍🍳👩🏻‍🍳👩🏻‍🍳👩🏻‍🍳
Recommend: 💖💖💖💖
Service: 💁🏻‍♀️💁🏻‍♀️💁🏻‍♀️
(Ratings out of 5)

reviews.text:
ネットから予約すると「Fumi（文）」という名で返信がある。え！予約した店間違ったかな！って思ったけど、でもこれで俺の割烹てお店で間違ってないっぽい。よくわかんない(笑)
名前が変わったのかもしれないけどメニューは美味しい日本食で間違いない。休日の11時半開店と同時に入店。貸し切りのようでのんびり食事を楽しめた。スタッフの女の子が会計時に「アリガトウ」ってニコってしてくれて気持ちもイイ。なぜもっと早くここに来なかったんだろう。リピート間違い無しです。

生日月份老友請吔飯🎉🎉 揀咗老蘭
FUMI, 仲要早到訂埋枱，真係唔話得🥳🥳

有訂枱下安排坐較靜既偏廳，燈光略暗😴但枱同枱既距離夠遠同埋枱面都夠闊放兩組大定食😏 

小弟揀咗天婦羅定食，原來定食本身已跟魚生🐟🐟四款魚生都無雪氣，肉質嫩滑，同平時其他日本午餐定食比有誠好多👍👍仲要砌到整齊上枱😍😍

然後定食仲有青瓜，蒸蛋同米飯，未算好出色，合格有餘👌蒸蛋未有盪口既溫度，小小失望，但米飯係和暖剛好

天婦羅有三隻蝦🦐🦐🦐夾埋其他時蔬🥬🥦🥒 全部炸得靚靚，無feel到油膩係中間，用料都唔差，食得出食材既鮮味😏

中午時份，中環核心，價錢就唔平架喇，不過作為午餐小聚聊天既高格調，係一個唔錯選擇👍👍

Food was great and I've enjoyed our food. However, the service needs to be improved  given their target audience based on their ambience and price tag. It's a far cry compared to the quality of food. 

Attentiveness on filling up the tea needs be consistently reminded, clearing the table was up to me before the next dish is served, and General lack of awareness from the staff does not match with the target audience they are aiming for. Every detail needs to be asked before it gets done.

The only Japanese restaurant in HK which passed my raw seafood handling test. Q1 your seafood fresh? Q2 have they been deep frozen? 
Guidelines requires raw fish to be frozen at -35C for 7 hours or -20C for 7 days to kill parasites and ova.

Food is mediocre & overpriced.  Although restaurant is listed on eatigo for a huge discount during off-peak hours, staff are extremely strict about the fine print of the discount. So don’t book on eatigo and expect a discount unless you’re sure you can finish your lunch strictly within 1 hour.

result.name: California Tower

reviews.text: Big tower. Good views on a clear night. Quite expensive but you’d expect that at the top!
Gorgeous rooftop bar, Ce La Vie on the very top floor! Beautiful views of Hong Kong.

Good selection of restaurants from the bottom floor to the top. Or if you want to get your sweat on then I'd highly recommend signing up for the Pure gym - chances are this is the closest one to those working in central. Top floors have pretty great views, particularly towards the south.
There's this bar located at the rooftop called Cest La Vie. A really nice bar to chill at! Love it!
Pure Fitness at California tower is the best gym in town!
